      "source": [
        "## Setup and Run GridSearchCV\n",
        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Initialize and execute a GridSearchCV to find the optimal hyperparameters for the XGBoost pipeline.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1969880c",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
